contentrichtext.text: '''Gillett''' is the name of several places in the United States: *[[Gillett, Arkansas]] *[[Gillett, Wisconsin]] *[[Gillett (town), Wisconsin]] *[[Gillett, Texas]] *[[Gillett Grove, Iowa]] '''Gillett''' as a surname may refer to: * [[Fred Gillett]], an astronomer who identified a planetary nebula in Messier 22 in 1986 * [[Frederick H. Gillett]], former US Speaker of the House, US Representative and US Senator from Massachusetts * [[James Gillett]], a Republican politician and 22nd Governor of California from 1907 to 1911 * [[George N. Gillett Jr.]], an American businessman, owner of various sports teams == See also == * [[Gillette (disambiguation)]] * [[Jillette]] {{disambig}} [[Category:Place name disambiguation pages]]
